    <briefdescription>
<para>struct XUsbPsu_event_depvt - Device Endpoint Events Device Endpoint Events </para>    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>Is_EpEvt</parametername>
<parametername>:</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>indicates this is an endpoint event </para></parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>endpoint_number</parametername>
<parametername>:</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>number of the endpoint </para></parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>endpoint_event</parametername>
<parametername>:</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The event we have: 0x00 - Reserved 0x01 - XferComplete 0x02 - XferInProgress 0x03 - XferNotReady 0x04 - RxTxFifoEvt (IN-&gt;Underrun, OUT-&gt;Overrun) 0x05 - Reserved 0x06 - StreamEvt 0x07 - EPCmdCmplt </para></parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>Reserved11_10</parametername>
<parametername>:</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Reserved, don&apos;t use. </para></parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>Status</parametername>
<parametername>:</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Indicates the status of the event. Refer to databook for more information. </para></parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>Parameters</parametername>
<parametername>:</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Parameters of the current event. Refer to databook for more information. </para></parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
</para>    </detaileddescription>
